original_title: Mat Moto: Kami Mat Moto Bukan Mat Rempit
overview: The film follows the journey of fellow "mat moto", also known as bikers, who share the same interest in motorsport. On a journey across Malaysia, the bikers discover the true meaning of friendship and the joy of sharing the same hobby.
title: Mat Moto: Kami Mat Moto Bukan Mat Rempit
